data.description: Breathtaking waterfront location right on the beach with huge entertainment deck overlooking the harbor. Watch the sailboats heading out to Penn Cove & enjoy a front row seat to sunrises over the bay. Panoramic view of the Cascade Mtns, Penn Cove & Mt Rainier in the distance. Updated throughout with granite counters & full tile backsplash, custom cabinetry, crown moldings & custom framed windows & doorways, gas fireplace, stainless appliances, spa-like master bath, jetted tub & walk-in shower. Walk to shopping & restaurants & enjoy the 80+ acre Windjammer Park right next door. Almost 1800 sq ft of indoor living space & additional 260 sq ft of outdoor decks. ADA elevator access, private 2 car garage, & direct beach access from the community!
